data.description: No Money down with the USDA 100 % financing. Welcome to the country! Adorable 3br 2bath home nestled back on 2.86 private acres. Bring your campers and all of your toys with plenty of space to store! Enter thru the front or side covered door into an inviting spacious living room right off of the dining room and open kitchen. Walk in laundry room located in the hallway. Spacious 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms that feature a vanity and tub shower combo in each. Carpeted flooring throughout and long-lasting vinyl in kitchen and baths. This property includes a fenced in back yard perfect for your loved pets, a separate storage shed with shelving and a level private lot to do anything your heart desires. This home is perfectly located only minutes to the I85 Grantville exit. This  home has access to High speed Internet
